  <description>
"Glory for the first man to die, CHARGE!"\n\nFight with or against the Cadian Shock Troops, Imperial Guard Regiments raised from the world of Cadia. For millenia, the armies of Cadia have stood bastion against the Eye of Terror, a duty which they held even as their homeworld crumbled beneath them. Scattered but unbroken, the Hammer of The Emperor comes to the edge of Imperial Space, ready to carry His holy light into the darkest of places. Wield the weapons and armor of The Imperium's most iconic guardsmen and shatter your foes with faith, steel, and lasguns. Cadia Stands! \n\nThis mod includes:\n- Apparels\n- Melee and ranged weapons\n- Defenses\n- Regimental faction\n- Structures\n- Vehicles (if the Vehicle Framework is enabled)\n\nHammer of the Imperium is a mod within the "Regiments of Renown" mini-series, from GrimWorld 40,000.
  </description>
